 org/w3c/dom/traversal/TreeWalker.java
+## See jv_convert_LDADD.
+lib_org_w3c_dom_la_LIBADD = -L$(here)/.libs libgcj.la
+lib_org_w3c_dom_la_LDFLAGS = -rpath $(toolexeclibdir) \

+        -version-info `grep -v '^\#' $(srcdir)/libtool-version`
